OL,5, Carnauba wax is a product you may not  
OL,6, have heard of, but you have almost     
OL,7, certainly consumed it - it is added to 
OL,8, sweets to stop them melting, to pills  
OL,9, to make them easier to swallow and as a
OL,10, thickener in lipstick and mascara.     
OL,12,FWorkers in Brazil's poor north-eastern 
OL,13,Fstate of Piaui rely on harvesting wax  
OL,14,Ffrom carnauba palm trees to earn a     
OL,15,Fliving. But the power is in the hands  
OL,16,Fof big business who, authorities say,  
OL,17,Fare turning a blind eye to             
OL,18,Fexploitation.                          
